metadata.name: Kratos Texticle
metadata.description:
Kratos is a fictional character portrayed by this typographic portrait. It took me 35 hours to make it using Adobe Illustrator. I used different sizes of Poppins font. 
As we know, Kratos is the protagonist and the prime mover of the God of War series, a popular video game series created by Santa Monica Studio. Kratos is considered a god of strength and power in Greek mythology.
